20
00:02:09.670 --> 00:02:12.465
<i>However, we must not compromise
territorial range.</i>

21
00:02:12.757 --> 00:02:15.593
<i>Remember that only
by following instructions</i>

22
00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:18.888
<i>can we hope to maintain
a successful highway program.</i>

23
00:02:19.055 --> 00:02:20.514
<i>Ah, Jesus!</i>

24
00:02:20.723 --> 00:02:23.934
<i>March Hare to Big Bopper.
We're three minutes off the intersection.</i>

25
00:02:24.018 --> 00:02:26.353
<i>- Reckon you can make it?</i>
- We'll make it! Move over!

26
00:02:26.437 --> 00:02:28.731
- Roop!
- I'm driving!

27
00:02:28.898 --> 00:02:30.858
