and takes off in a Pursuit Special.</i>

34
00:02:52.046 --> 00:02:54.298
<i>We've been on him ever since.</i>

35
00:02:54.715 --> 00:02:56.759
<i>This one's as flaky as they come, Roop.</i>

36
