38
00:03:08.104 --> 00:03:10.731
<i>That's what hurts. It's one of our V8s.</i>

39
00:03:11.190 --> 00:03:14.193
<i>Pursuit Special on methane. Super hot!</i>

40
00:03:22.409 --> 00:03:24.411
Okay, we're about half a mile
off Anarchy Road.

41
00:03:24.495 --> 00:03:26.580
