53
00:04:19.341 --> 00:04:21.385
Do you see me, man?

54
00:04:24.305 --> 00:04:27.099
Keep going. Keep going, we're okay.

55
00:04:27.975 --> 00:04:29.518
We got you, we're going.

56
00:04:34.023 --> 00:04:36.150
Born with a steering wheel in his hand,

57
