89
00:07:37.831 --> 00:07:39.083
He's gone.

90
00:07:39.249 --> 00:07:40.292
Bastard!

91
00:07:41.960 --> 00:07:43.879
Oh, shit!

92
00:07:44.463 --> 00:07:46.840
You're really gonna get it this time.
He had his indicator on.

93
00:07:46.924 --> 00:07:47.925
Shut up!

94
00:07:52.262 --> 00:07:54.681
No, no, you're not going on.
Stay off the road!

95
00:07:54.848 --> 00:07:56.433
Of course, I'm going on. Shut up!

96
00:07:56.517 --> 00:07:58.143
People's lives are in peril!

97
00:07:59.478 --> 00:08:01.688
What are you doing? You gone nuts?

98
00:08:07.277 --> 00:08:09.071
Do I have him?

99
00:08:10.781 --> 00:08:13.242
Stay off the road!

100
00:08:15.994 --> 00:08:18.330
- I got him! Shut up!
- Stay on him!

101
00:08:29.675 --> 00:08:31.677
Oh, my God.

102
00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.305
Watch out!

103
00:08:45.274 --> 00:08:47.693
- Great! Down in one.
- Ha-ha-ha!

104
00:08:52.030 --> 00:08:53.574
<i>I am ready.</i>

105
00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:56.201
<i>I am ready for your best.</i>

106
00:08:57.953 --> 00:08:59.455
Oh, my God, what happened?

107
00:08:59.621 --> 00:09:01.721
I don't know, man. I just got here myself.

108
00:09:08.130 --> 00:09:09.715
Main Force Patrol

109
00:09:10.007 --> 00:09:11.467
we're out of the game

110
00:09:11.633 --> 00:09:14.052
