111
00:09:14.845 --> 00:09:16.346
You'd better send a meat truck.

112
00:09:16.430 --> 00:09:18.098
Charlie's been hurt bad in the throat.

113
00:09:18.182 --> 00:09:19.224
Hey, Max?

114
00:09:20.767 --> 00:09:22.561
<i>Can you hear me, Max?</i>

115
00:09:22.895 --> 00:09:24.188
Go ahead.

116
00:09:24.396 --> 00:09:26.690
<i>We are 100 percent snafued.</i>

117
00:09:26.982 --> 00:09:27.983
You okay, Goose?

118
00:09:28.150 --> 00:09:30.819
Nothing a year in
the tropics wouldn't fix!

119
00:09:31.195 --> 00:09:32.279
Much damage?

120
00:09:34.907 --> 00:09:38.035
You should see the damage, Bronze! Huh?

121
00:09:38.202 --> 00:09:39.286
Metal damage

122
00:09:39.453 --> 00:09:41.622
<i>brain damage, huh?
You listening, Bronze?</i>

123
00:09:42.247 --> 00:09:44.291
I am the Nightrider!

124
00:09:47.085 --> 00:09:49.963
I'm a fuel-injected suicide machine.

125
00:09:51.632 --> 00:09:57.804
I am a rocker! I am a roller!
I am an out-of-controller!

126
00:09:58.805 --> 00:10:00.682
I am a Nightrider, baby,

127
00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:05.521
<i>and it's me and my Marmaduke,
and we ain't never coming back.</i>

128
00:10:22.371 --> 00:10:23.830
The Toecutter

129
00:10:23.997 --> 00:10:25.457
he knows who I am.

130
00:10:25.832 --> 00:10:27.960
I am the Nightrider!

131
00:10:34.675 --> 00:10:38.387
I am the chosen one,
the mighty hand of vengeance

132
00:10:38.554 --> 00:10:42.724
<i>sent down to strike the unroadworthy!
Ha-ha-ha!</i>

133
00:10:42.891 --> 00:10:45.602
I'm hotter than a rolling dice.

134
00:10:45.769 --> 00:10:46.895
Step right up, chum,

135
00:10:47.062 --> 00:10:48.212
