137
00:11:30.897 --> 00:11:33.442
What's wrong? Baby, what's wrong?

138
00:11:36.236 --> 00:11:37.571
Tell me what's wrong!

139
00:11:51.001 --> 00:11:52.252
It's going.

140
00:11:52.544 --> 00:11:56.089
