144
00:13:13.083 --> 00:13:15.126
I got a right hook in the mouth
this morning.

145
00:13:15.210 --> 00:13:16.628
- Sprog?
- Mm.

146
00:13:16.795 --> 00:13:19.131
I told him to always lead with his left.

147
00:13:19.297 --> 00:13:22.092
You know, I think we've got
a monster on our hands.

148
